<ProsePage
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How HomeStem collects, uses, and protects your information."
  updated="June 2026"
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how HomeStem ("we", "us") handles information
    when you visit homeandstem.com. By using the site, you agree to the
    practices described here.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <p>
    We collect anonymous usage data — such as pages visited, browser type, and
    referring source — through analytics tools to understand how visitors use
    the site. We do not require you to create an account or submit personal
    information to read our content.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
  <p>
    HomeStem uses cookies and similar technologies, including Google Analytics
    and Google Tag Manager, to measure traffic and improve the site. You can
    disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    Some links on HomeStem are affiliate links, primarily through the Amazon
    Associates program. When you click these links, the destination site may set
    its own cookies. See our
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    We rely on third-party services (such as Amazon, Google, and our hosting
    provider) that have their own privacy policies governing how they handle
    your data.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Disable cookies through your browser settings.</li>
    <li>Use browser extensions to block analytics and tracking.</li>
    <li>Opt out of Google Analytics with Google's official browser add-on.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions about this policy, email us at
    <a href="mailto:homeandstem@gmail.com">homeandstem@gmail.com</a>.
  </p>
</ProsePage>
